34
00:03:07,420 --> 00:03:09,050
I have only one question.


35
00:03:10,830 --> 00:03:14,000
Is Jiu Liu Yu of the Qisha Valley
still here?


36
00:03:15,710 --> 00:03:16,680
Saintess.


37
00:03:17,260 --> 00:03:18,450
Master Jiu Liu Yu


38
