45
00:03:51,250 --> 00:03:52,790
They're back at the Qisha Valley.


46
00:03:53,420 --> 00:03:54,780
I'll go back and ask them.


47
00:03:55,770 --> 00:03:57,180
Are you planning to escape?


48
