101
00:06:13,940 --> 00:06:15,040
Get some sleep.


102
00:06:15,610 --> 00:06:17,320
You have plenty of things to do.


103
00:06:17,630 --> 00:06:19,040
Leave me be.


104
00:06:19,950 --> 00:06:21,710
Nothing is more important than you.


105
00:06:23,220 --> 00:06:25,820
